00:20:39,665 --> 00:20:43,760
Or someone else besides him?

283
00:20:45,356 --> 00:20:46,640
<i>I'm talking about...</i>

284
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,360
<i>my name.</i>

285
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,360
<i>Fang Chi.</i>

286
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:55,160
<i>Fang Chi.</i>

287
00:20:58,126 --> 00:20:59,846
Excluding me.

288
00:21:03,428 --> 00:21:05,860
N-No.

289
00:21:09,406 --> 00:21:11,646
You seem a little nervous.

290
00:21:12,977 --> 00:21:14,477
I...

291
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,966
I'm...

292
00:21:16,966 --> 00:21:19,086
Don't lie to me.

293
00:21:20,726 --> 00:21:22,486
You want me to bring the pointer?

294
00:21:22,486 --> 00:21:24,006
I was wrong.

295
00:21:25,406 --> 00:21:27,166
Only once.

296
00:21:27,886 --> 00:21:29,686
Only once...

297
00:21:31,526 --> 00:21:33,680
It was Justin.

298
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,520
Why him?

299
00:21:36,226 --> 00:21:38,480
There was an auction.

300
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,402
He had too much to drink at the dinner party.

301
00:21:40,402 --> 00:21:42,402
On his way back to his room,

302
00:21:43,766 --> 00:21:46,763
he tried to hold me back, but I avoided him.

303
00:21:46,763 --> 00:21:50,596
That night, I had a nightmare.

304
00:21:50,596 --> 00:21:52,646
In my dream, I fought back.

305
00:21:52,646 --> 00:21:55,206
But he didn't let me go.

306
00:21:55,206 --> 00:21:57,446
Did you feel pleasure in your dreams?

307
00:21:58,206 --> 00:22:00,246
Not with them.

308
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,520
In my dream,

309
00:22:07,029 --> 00:22:08,669
I only feel pleasure...

310
00:22:10,286 --> 00:22:12,326
only with you.

311
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:16,126
Because I want to.

312
00:22:16,126 --> 00:22:19,206
What? What's this nonsense?

313
00:22:19,966 --> 00:22:21,360
I'm sorry.

314
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:23,686
I've tainted you.

315
00:22:23,686 --> 00:22:26,548
I'm shameless. I'm sick.

316
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:33,926
But when I saw it was your face, I just...

317
00:22:33,926 --> 00:22:35,526
Go on.

318
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:37,780
I want to hear it.

319
00:22:38,886 --> 00:22:41,966
At first, I couldn't believe it.

320
00:22:41,966 --> 00:22:44,926
Until I touched your face.

321
00:22:44,926 --> 00:22:46,846
Even if it was a dream,

322
00:22:47,966 --> 00:22:50,206
I just wanted to hold you.

323
00:22:51,046 --> 00:22:53,046
And cry on your shoulder.

324
00:22:54,926 --> 00:22:56,646
Why did you cry?

325
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:01,080
Because...

326
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:06,480
you finally came to my rescue.

327
00:23:34,806 --> 00:23:37,606
I'm glad you're brave enough to ride in a car.

328
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:41,440
That's because you're the one in the car.

329
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:44,904
Do you want me to walk you up?

330
00:23:44,904 --> 00:23:47,000
No.

331
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,806
If it's on your way,

332
00:23:49,806 --> 00:23:51,926
you can come and have coffee with me anytime.

333
00:23:51,926 --> 00:23:53,446
Won't that trouble you?

334
00:23:53,446 --> 00:23:54,946
Not at all.

335
00:23:58,686 --> 00:24:00,126
I can't wait for you to come.

336
00:24:00,126 --> 00:24:01,280
What?

337
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,800
Nothing.

338
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:06,360
Dr Fang.

339
00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:08,040
See you next time.

340
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,350
Hello, do you have an appointment?

341
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:26,606
I'm a friend of Mr Gao Zhun.

342
00:25:26,606 --> 00:25:28,400
He left something in my car.

343
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,080
Please wait a moment.

344
00:25:35,320 --> 00:25:37,170
Mr. Gao isn't picking up

345
00:25:37,170 --> 00:25:39,120
I understand. I'll just wait here.

346
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:41,279
Why don't you come in?

347
00:25:41,279 --> 00:25:42,760
This way.

348
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:45,479
Mr. Gao and Mr. Jia are having
a meeting in the conference room.

349
00:25:45,479 --> 00:25:48,520
Once the meeting is over,
I'll inform you immediately.

350
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:50,020
This way, please.
[Justin, Jia Shao Ting, Research Manager]

351
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:53,560
<i>I want to...</i>

352
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:58,570
<i>find an opportunity to corner him.</i>

353
00:26:01,170 --> 00:26:04,960
Excuse me, is this Mr. Jia
who's having a meeting with Mr. Gao?

354
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,920
Yes, Mr. Jia is from our company.

355
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,677
Where are they meeting?

356
00:26:08,677 --> 00:26:10,560
The conference room on the eighth floor.

357
00:26:10,560 --> 00:26:13,040
Sir, what are you doing?

358
00:26:26,730 --> 00:26:27,730
Where is the conference room?

359
00:26:27,730 --> 00:26:29,727
Over there.

360
00:26:29,727 --> 00:26:31,401
Who is he?

361
00:26:45,050 --> 00:26:46,690
Dr. Fang.

362
00:26:48,010 --> 00:26:50,250
What are you...

363
00:26:52,930 --> 00:26:54,490
Come with me.

364
00:26:58,410 --> 00:27:00,370
What's going on?

365
00:27:06,730 --> 00:27:08,490
Let's continue the meeting.

366
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:17,730
Why didn't you answer my calls?

367
00:27:17,730 --> 00:27:18,930
I was in a meeting.

368
00:27:18,930 --> 00:27:21,170
I put my phone on silent mode.

369
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,930
Are you free today?

370
00:27:48,930 --> 00:27:50,120
Yes.

371
00:27:50,120 --> 00:27:52,880
I always have time for you.

372
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:56,800
Then come with me.

373
00:27:58,298 --> 00:28:00,690
I just remembered.

374
00:28:00,690 --> 00:28:02,930
You have one more checkup to do.

375
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:08,460
Okay.

376
00:28:09,930 --> 00:28:11,930
Dr. Fang.

377
00:28:11,930 --> 00:28:15,850
I'm glad you came to see me.

378
00:28:35,570 --> 00:28:37,210
Don't be afraid.

379
00:28:37,930 --> 00:28:39,770
I'm here with you.

380
00:28:42,290 --> 00:28:44,290
If I really am down with it...

381
00:28:46,250 --> 00:28:47,890
Just leave me be.

382
00:28:49,530 --> 00:28:51,370
Let me die.

383
00:28:54,370 --> 00:28:56,250
It's going to be okay.

384
00:28:56,880 --> 00:29:00,040
Wow, two guys holding hands.

385
00:29:03,010 --> 00:29:05,010
Don't worry about what they think.

386
00:29:05,685 --> 00:29:08,165
I only care about how you feel.

387
00:29:25,050 --> 00:29:26,525
It won't take long.

388
00:29:27,810 --> 00:29:29,610
It doesn't hurt that much.

389
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:40,580
Press it.

390
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:44,050
I can do it myself.

391
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:46,570
I'll bleed.

392
00:29:46,570 --> 00:29:47,960
What if...

393
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,330
Your hand.

394
00:29:49,330 --> 00:29:51,050
Give it to me.

395
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:05,930
Don't worry.

396
00:30:05,930 --> 00:30:08,410
I'll be by your side no matter what.

397
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:13,290
I'm going to get the report.

398
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:18,320
Your boyfriend is so good to you.

399
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:21,680
He's not your boyfriend?

400
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,930
No.

401
00:30:24,930 --> 00:30:26,734
He's my doctor.

402
00:30:26,734 --> 00:30:28,200
Doctor?

403
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:30,680
The kind who gives injections at night, right?

404
00:30:40,290 --> 00:30:41,530
What's wrong?

405
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:43,680
Are you scared?

406
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,610
Are you a doctor?

407
00:30:45,610 --> 00:30:46,970
Yes.

408
00:30:46,970 --> 00:30:48,284
A psychiatrist.

409
00:30:48,284 --> 00:30:49,517
I see.

410
00:30:49,517 --> 00:30:52,490
I can come to you
for psychological problems, too.

411
00:30:52,490 --> 00:30:54,831
I have insomnia and nightmares.

412
00:30:54,831 --> 00:30:56,770
I don't know what to do.

413
00:30:56,770 --> 00:30:59,040
You can come for a consultation.

414
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,775
It's free for the first time.

415
00:31:00,775 --> 00:31:03,415
Then can I have your number?

416
00:31:09,050 --> 00:31:11,355
Call me if you need a consultation.

417
00:31:11,355 --> 00:31:12,642
Okay.

418
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:20,043
<i>However, if you ever need help,
you can call me, too.</i>

419
00:31:21,130 --> 00:31:23,330
<i>Even if it's three in the morning.</i>

420
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,960
What's wrong?

421
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:33,050
Mr. Gao.

422
00:31:33,050 --> 00:31:34,690
Gao Zhun.

423
00:31:34,690 --> 00:31:36,560
Look at me.

424
00:31:36,560 --> 00:31:38,800
A tiff?

425
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:45,130
Did they say something?

426
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:48,640
Are you afraid they'll think
we're in a relationship?

427
00:31:54,010 --> 00:31:56,290
They're all alone.

428
00:31:56,290 --> 00:31:58,770
So-called friends and friends with benefits.

429
00:31:58,770 --> 00:32:01,290
They didn't come with any of these people.

430
00:32:01,290 --> 00:32:03,210
But you have me.

431
00:32:04,210 --> 00:32:05,937
That's why they're jealous.

432
00:32:06,930 --> 00:32:08,650
Don't overthink it.

433
00:32:09,450 --> 00:32:11,170
Do you understand?

434
00:32:14,290 --> 00:32:16,010
So, we're...

435
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:23,046
You're safe.

436
00:32:31,130 --> 00:32:32,850
It's okay.

437
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,885
Thank you.

438
00:32:44,885 --> 00:32:46,385
Doctor...

439
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:50,210
Dr. Fang.

440
00:33:08,770 --> 00:33:11,530
<i>Are you afraid they'll think
we're in a relationship?</i>

441
00:33:14,450 --> 00:33:17,867
<i>If you ever need help,
you can call me, too.</i>

442
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:20,560
Call?

443
00:33:21,812 --> 00:33:23,658
I can call.

444
00:33:23,658 --> 00:33:25,858
Someone else can do that, too.

445
00:33:27,332 --> 00:33:29,280
It doesn't matter who it is.

446
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:31,480
Anyone can do that.

447
00:33:32,290 --> 00:33:35,400
I'm not afraid they'll guess our relationship.

448
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:37,210
I'm just afraid...

449
00:33:37,210 --> 00:33:38,770
I'm afraid...

450
00:33:39,487 --> 00:33:41,487
I'm afraid that once I'm better,

451
00:33:43,342 --> 00:33:45,523
we'll go our separate ways.

452
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:21,964
<i>Mr. Gao.</i>

453
00:34:21,964 --> 00:34:25,764
<i>Writing letters to patients
is a form of narrative therapy.</i>

454
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,842
<i>For others,</i>

455
00:34:27,842 --> 00:34:31,002
<i>I usually repeat the treatment at the clinic.</i>

456
00:34:31,709 --> 00:34:34,069
<i>But this time, it's for you.</i>

457
00:34:34,680 --> 00:34:36,680
<i>I think it's a bit different.</i>

458
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,841
<i>Mr. Gao.</i>

459
00:34:39,841 --> 00:34:43,240
<i>Do you want to know
what you look like in my mind?</i>

460
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:45,107
<i>Remember that exhibition?</i>

461
00:34:45,107 --> 00:34:47,938
<i>You were waiting for me in the dark.</i>

462
00:34:47,938 --> 00:34:49,738
<i>It's me.</i>

463
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:53,381
<i>Remember the contact exercises?</i>

464
00:34:53,381 --> 00:34:55,063
<i>You were so scared.</i>

465
00:34:55,063 --> 00:34:57,558
<i>But you didn't run away.</i>

466
00:34:57,558 --> 00:34:59,558
<i>Don't be scared.</i>

467
00:34:59,558 --> 00:35:01,438
<i>It's okay.</i>

468
00:35:01,438 --> 00:35:04,198
<i>Remember the fireworks
and the fountain at the Qixi Festival?</i>

469
00:35:04,198 --> 00:35:06,916
<i>You were brave enough to tell me your story.</i>

470
00:35:07,878 --> 00:35:10,520
<i>What I remember most about you</i>

471
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:13,234
<i>was your courage to risk your life.</i>

472
00:35:14,078 --> 00:35:15,918
<i>And your beauty.</i>

473
00:35:17,158 --> 00:35:20,878
<i>Maybe beauty is not
the right word to describe a man.</i>

474
00:35:20,878 --> 00:35:22,962
<i>But you are beautiful.</i>

475
00:35:22,962 --> 00:35:26,762
<i>You're like a beautiful flower.</i>

476
00:35:27,682 --> 00:35:30,282
<i>Beauty has caused you
to suffer some bad experiences.</i>

477
00:35:30,282 --> 00:35:32,162
<i>But you should know this.</i>

478
00:35:32,162 --> 00:35:34,322
<i>Beauty is not something to be blamed for.</i>

479
00:35:35,682 --> 00:35:37,682
<i>The last thing I want to see</i>

480
00:35:37,682 --> 00:35:40,446
<i>is you torturing yourself
for someone else's sins.</i>

481
00:35:41,522 --> 00:35:45,082
<i>I'm most afraid of hearing
the word "death" from you.</i>

482
00:35:46,922 --> 00:35:49,200
<i>Lastly,</i>

483
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:51,893
<i>thank you for your trust
and cooperation all this time.</i>

484
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:55,760
<i>No matter how unreasonable my request was,</i>

485
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:58,350
<i>you'd always give in to me.</i>

486
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:03,000
<i>More than once,
I thought that meeting you</i>

487
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:05,983
<i>was one of the biggest gains of my life.</i>

488
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:10,914
<i>Thank you, Gao Zhun.</i>

489
00:36:40,110 --> 00:36:42,051
[Gao Zhun]

490
00:36:47,544 --> 00:36:51,335
[Gao Zhun]

491
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,775
Mr. Gao.

492
00:37:00,775 --> 00:37:03,240
It's late.

493
00:37:03,240 --> 00:37:05,120
What's the matter?

494
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,920
<i>The letter.</i>

495
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:10,532
<i>I received it.</i>

496
00:37:12,350 --> 00:37:13,910
I'm sorry.

497
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:17,400
I shouldn't have sulked.

498
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,680
Why did you sulk?

499
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:21,440
<i>I just...</i>

500
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:28,600
I couldn't stand that you gave
that boy your business card.

501
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:31,760
I can't stand it when you're as good
to others as you are to me.

502
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:36,200
I just want you to be good to me.

503
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:39,560
<i>I just want you to look at me.</i>

504
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,980
<i>I...</i>

505
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:49,560
I get jealous.

506
00:41:39,537 --> 00:41:40,720
Mr. Jia.

507
00:41:40,720 --> 00:41:42,680
Please calm down.

508
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:48,054
As you can see, I didn't go there to see you.

509
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,090
Right.

510
00:41:51,090 --> 00:41:52,970
It's a coincidence.

511
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:55,901
Don't worry.

512
00:41:58,280 --> 00:42:00,070
I'm a doctor.

513
00:42:00,070 --> 00:42:03,150
I have to protect my client's privacy.

514
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,346
Yes.

515
00:42:06,346 --> 00:42:10,053
He doesn't know that you're my client.

